	(109,'Thailand',NULL,'','','<p>Thailand is one of the most famous countries for Tourism in Asia. As the political, economic, cultural, culinary, and spiritual capital of Thailand, Bangkok features both old-world charm and modern convenience, at times served up in an apparently chaotic manner, but always with a gracious smile. Regent Holidays currently offers packages in many major destinations of Thailand including Bangkok, Pattaya, Phuket, Chiang Mai, Koh Samui,Krabi Hua Hin, Chiang Rai, Ko Chang, Surat Thani etc. All of these destinations are distinct fromeach other. Tourists from all over the world visit Thailand for treatment round the year. Bangkok has many sightseeing options for travelers. Major sightseeing includes Safari world tour, Dream world tour, Madame Tussauds museum, Alcazar show, River Cruse. Tourist may choose sightseeing according to their taste. Travelers never get bored during their stay in Bangkok. There are plenty of options for shopping as shopping place starts from street to some of Asia.s biggest malls like Central World, Siam Paragon, MBK. Bangkok offers shopping, facility to everyone according to their choice &amp; budget. Thai Cuisine is world famous. Food lovers have plenty of options for checking the local foods. Streets are full of variety of Thai &amp; other foods in reasonable price. Not just cooked foods there are different seasonal fresh fruits available all over Thailand. Medical tourism in Thailand is very famous. There are hospitals like Bangkok Nursing Home Hospital Bumrungrad International Hospital, Samitivej Sukhumvit Hospital, Bangkok International Hospital with high quality medical care in reasonable price. Hospitals in Thailand provide personal care.</p>',NULL,'package-details','Thailand.jpg',NULL,'2018-03-11 08:29:54','2018-03-11 08:29:54',1,'','',2,NULL),
	(110,'Malaysia',NULL,'','','<p>Malaysia is one of the south East Asia.s major tourist countries. With low living cost &amp; year round tropical climate, Malaysia remains a favorite destination for travelers all over the world. Malaysia is a nation rich in diversity. In Malaysia- Male, Chinese, Indigenous, Indian &amp; small ethnic group live together in respectful harmony. It.s diverse cultural heritage add spice &amp; color to every aspect of life here. This is a country of geographical diversity. Regent Holidays cover destinations in Malaysia as Kuala Lumpur, Genting Highlands, Penang,Langkawi etc. Most of the tourist enters Malaysia via Kuala Lumpur. Other places of tourist attractions are Cameron Highlands, Malacca, Tioman Island, Selangor. All of these destinations are well equipped with amenities for tourists. Medical facility is also becoming better day by day. Malaysia is attracting patients from around the world for better treatment in reasonable price. For most of tourists, shopping is a great experience in Malaysia. Only in Kuala Lumpur there are over 50 shopping malls. Luxurious shopping malls in Malaysia offer products in affordable price though bargaining is not an option for shopping malls. Bargaining is an option for doing shopping in night markets. Most mentionable night market is Chinatown, along Petaling street. Travelers love to buy bags, shoes, accessories, sunglasses, copy watches from these markets. There are plenty of hawkers around the streets of Kuala Lumpur as well. Malaysia is a country with a lot of activities to do. Major sightseeing places are Genting Highlands, Putrajaya, KL Tower, Petronas Tower, Beaches in Penang-Langkawi etc.</p>',NULL,'package-details','kualalumpur2.jpg',NULL,'2018-03-11 08:30:14','2018-03-11 08:30:14',1,'','',3,NULL),
	(111,'Singapore',NULL,'','','<p>Singapore was the jewel in Britain.s empire. The global commerce, transportation and financial hub, the top choice for Tourist. Singapore has taken the development in such a level that, it is one the four Asian economic tigers. Regent Holidays offers package within in the Singapore city as well in Sentosa Island. Across the cities most attractive places of the town for their unique features are China town-famous for restaurants, boutique hotels &amp; gift shops, street market, Little India-colorful, gods of Hindu, nearby Male &amp; Muslim quarter&nbsp;has handicrafts from the Arabian World. Singapore has some of the most magnificent architectural creation of 21st century. Marina bay shines in the sky of Singapore. On the other hand Garden by the Bay is reflection of mankind.s flowering imagination. Singapore earned reputation for high quality medical treatment for a very long time. One thing unites all Singaporean that is food. It.s a national obsession for Singaporean. Besides foreign foods, local foods are quite famous here like Makan, Sate smoke. Despite Singapore high urban density, the Island is very fertile. Escape the heat &amp; enter the world of color, the Singapore botanic garden &amp; the national orchid garden. The jungle part is quite diverse in Singapore. Singapore zoo is a home to over 300 species. Jurong bird park is attracting travelers for over 40 years. Another Singaporean obsession is shopping. Orchard road is full of exclusive outlets. To change the taste, head to the Bugis market to buy goods if you have plenty of time. To pass a day with full of excitement, Sentosa is the best option in Singapore. An Island playground filled with resort, theme parks, beaches &amp; bars. The western tip of the Island-Fort Siloso reminds the darkest days of Singapore during World War 2.Singapore is the example of making a small destination into a giant.</p>',NULL,'package-details','Singapore2.jpg',NULL,'2018-03-11 08:32:04','2018-03-11 08:32:04',1,'','',4,NULL),
